Package com.solus.integrationlibrary.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IBaseApiListener<T>
    Used for the api requests to handle the server response
    IWorkflowProccessListener
    The main listener of the workflow process, which helps to control the whole process and track the process actions as abort, error or successful complete
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    ApiErrorCode  
    ApplicationCode  
    PendingActivity
    Each workflow process consist of few stages - pending activities, which returns from the server and should be processed on the mobile side and returns the data back to the server through the method:
    WorkflowStatus
    During workflow process, server returns the status of the workflow, which determines the future handling of the API response inside the integration library
